      <procstep>
        <procdesc>The Major Cities layer in the Global GIS database was created by extracting populated places with native names only which gave us 9498 of 2095063. Then to reduce the set further we extracted only the cities with the feature code of "Capital of first order administrative division (PPLA)" or "Capital of Country" (PPLC). This left many large populated cities off the list. To help account for the larger populated cities, we merged some data from the ESRI World Cities database. Any city without a Gaz_name entry in the table was merged from the ESRI dataset ESRI. For the North America tile and Global DVD we added the Major Cities database from the National Atlas (Geographic Names Information System ) for US names. The US Fips code was saved in the Unique_nam field. The Gaz_name field contains the original string from the Full_name field. The Full_name field was processed to replace some of the unrecognizable diacritical symbols.</procdesc>
